           move      "PE"                 to   v-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Esecuzione del programma                        *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   prn-rou-pri-000      thru prn-rou-pri-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Cancellazione messaggio                         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "XE"                 to   v-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
